SARS-CoV-2 vaccine effectiveness assessment (synthetic dataset 10k)

Description: Synthetic data set to test the causal model proposed by the baseline use case in BY-COVID WP5 assessing the effectiveness of the SARS-CoV-2 vaccine (10k registries and 650k registries)

Bibliographic

Published 26-01-2023

Coverage

Temporal

End 31-12-2024

Spatial

Attributes

Name Description Unit
person_id Pseudoid of the person included in the cohort
age_nm Age of the person included in the cohort (at the time of entering the cohort) years
sex_cd Sex of the person included in the cohort (at the time of entering the cohort)
socecon_lvl_cd Socioeconomic level of the person in the cohort (at the time of entering the cohort)
residence_area_cd Area of residence of the person included in the cohort (NUTS 3) (at the time of entering the cohort)
country_cd Country of residence of the person included in the cohort (at the time of entering the cohort)
foreign_bl Is the country of residence different from the country that is doing the analyses?
exitus_dt Date of death of the person (if the person has died)
exitus_bl Date of death of the person (if the person has died during the period of study)
essential_worker_bl Is the person included in the cohort an essential worker? (at the time of entering the cohort)
institutionalized_bl Is the person included in the cohort institutionalized? (at the time of entering the cohort)
dose_1_brand_cd Brand of first dose of the vaccine
dose_1_dt Date of the first dose of the vaccine
dose_2_brand_cd Brand of second dose of the vaccine
dose_2_dt Date of the second dose of the vaccine
dose_3_brand_cd Brand of third dose of the vaccine
dose_3_dt Date of the third dose of the vaccine
number_doses Number of doses (independently of the vaccine brand) received by a person during the period of study
fully_vaccinated_dt Date on which the person included in the cohort is considered fully vaccinated
fully_vaccinated_bl Is the person included in the cohort fully vaccinated?
vaccination_schedule_cd Vaccine types received for 1st and 2nd dose concatenated with hyphen
confirmed_case_dt Date of diagnosis or date of test result positive of any known/confirmed infection after 2021-01-01 (SARS-CoV-2 vaccine roll-out) for non-vaccinated or after the person is considered fully vaccinated (see 'fully_vaccinated_dt') if vaccinated
confirmed_case_bl Is the person included in the cohort a confirmed COVID-19 case?
previous_infection_dt If the person experienced a confirmed infection before 2021-01-01 (SARS-CoV-2 vaccine roll-out) or before being considered fully vaccinated (see 'fully_vaccinated_dt')
previous_infection_bl Did the person experience a confirmed infection proceeding the last confirmed infection?
test_type_cd Type of COVID-19 test used to detect the last known SARS-CoV-2 infection (i.e. first positive test for SARS-CoV-2)
variant_cd Identified variant (WHO label) for last known SARS-CoV-2 infection
diabetes_bl Does the person included in the cohort suffer from type II diabetes (at the time of entering the cohort)?
obesity_bl Does the person included in the cohort suffer from obesity (at the time of entering the cohort)? 
heart_failure_bl Does the person included in the cohort suffer from heart failure (at the time of entering the cohort)?
copd_bl Does the person included in the cohort suffer from chronic lung disease (at the time of entering the cohort)?
solid_tumor_without_metastasis_bl Does the person included in the cohort suffer from solid cancer without metastatis (at the time of entering the cohort)?
chronic_kidney_disease_bl Does the person included in the cohort suffer from chronic kidney disease (at the time of entering the cohort)?
sickle_cell_disease_bl Does the person included in the cohort suffer from sickle cell disease (at the time of entering the cohort)?
hypertension_bl Does the person included in the cohort suffer from hypertension (at the time of entering the cohort)?
chronic_liver_disease_bl Does the person included in the cohort suffer from chronic liver disease (at the time of entering the cohort)?
blood_cancer_bl Does the person included in the cohort suffer from blood cancer (leukemia) (at the time of entering the cohort)?
transplanted_bl Is the person included in the cohort a transplant patient (i.e. solid organ transplantation) (at the time of entering the cohort)?
hiv_infection_bl Does the person included in the cohort suffer from a HIV infection (at the time of entering the cohort)?
primary_immunodeficiency_bl Does the person included in the cohort suffer from a primary immuno deficiency disease (lymphoma) (at the time of entering the cohort)?
immunosuppression_bl Does the person included in the cohort suffer from drugs induced immunosuppression (at the time of entering the cohort)?
pregnancy_bl Is the person included in the cohort pregnant (at the time of entering the cohort)?
